    <list id="import-auto-id1166922501357" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
      <item>
        <emphasis effect="bold">USE THE FORMAL OUTLINE TO BEGIN COLLECTING PUBLISHED SOURCES FOR YOUR PAPER.</emphasis>
      </item>
      <item>
        <emphasis effect="bold">CHOOSE ONE OF THE TWO APPROACHES FOR YOUR PAPER: </emphasis>
      </item>
    </list>
    <figure id="import-auto-id1166930432906">
